   Envirofacts (EPA)
   http://www.epa.gov/enviro/index_java.html
   The Envirofacts Warehouse gives you direct access to the wealth of
   environmental information in EPA's databases. Search by type of info,
   location, create reports, even generate environmental maps!
   Related Topics: Environment  Housing, health, and the environment
   Academic resources
