   Volunteer Paralegal and Intern Positions (US Dept of Justice)
   http://www.usdoj.gov/enrd/undergrad.htm
   Are you interested in interning or volunteering as a paralegal for the
   Dept of Justice? The Environmental and Natural Resources Division under
   the Dept of Justice offers volunteer paralegal and intern
   opportunities.
   Related Topics: Internships  Environment
